  "rationale": "The page follows a decision journey rather than the Remote homepage sequence: operational pain, product capability, workflow, audience-specific value, comparison, proof, trust, FAQ, and qualification. It reuses Remote\u2019s noise-panel hero, light canvas, inset dark media wells, deep-accent disclosure state, restrained proof treatment, and pill actions without copying the homepage narrative."
